\par \pard\plain \s0\sl254\slmult1\ql{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa160\ltrpar\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af4\afs24\lang1081\loch\f4\fs22\lang1046\sl360\slmult1\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi1418\sb0\sa0{\cf1\hich\af2\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f2
Os valores de FGTS dever\'e3o ser depositados na conta vinculada do trabalhador, em observ\'e2ncia ao disposto no art. 26, par\'e1grafo \'fanico, da Lei 8.036/90.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\sl254\slmult1\ql{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\sb0\sa160\ltrpar\nowidctlpar\cf0\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af4\afs24\lang1081\loch\f4\fs22\lang1046\sl360\slmult1\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi1418\sb0\sa0{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
}
